    "body": "Hi,\r\n\r\npublished NPM packages should not be bundled to allow bundlers like Browserify or Webpack or NodeJS runtime consuming them. You can't `require` already bundled module. Packages published to NPM should be bundler agnostic.\r\n\r\nYou should publish your package with \"dist\" code transpiled to ES5 using Babel and optionally with ES2015+ source code.",
